Subject: [PATCH] serial: zs: Convert to use a platform device
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 7.0.12
Git-commit: 7cac59d08a73cb866ec51a483a6f3fe0f531947c

commit 7cac59d08a73cb866ec51a483a6f3fe0f531947c upstream.

